TITLE: Configuring Native Modules for Lynx-View
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to set up nativeModulesMap for a lynx-view component. This creates a custom module that implements a getColor method which can communicate with native functionality and return results via callback.
SOURCE: https://github.com/lynx-family/lynx-stack/blob/main/packages/web-platform/web-worker-runtime/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const nativeModulesMap = {
  CustomModule: URL.createObjectURL(
    new Blob(
      [
        `export default function(NativeModules, NativeModulesCall) {
      return {
        async getColor(data, callback) {
          const color = await NativeModulesCall('getColor', data);
          callback(color);
        },
      }
    };`,
      ],
      { type: 'text/javascript' },
    ),
  ),
};
lynxView.nativeModulesMap = nativeModulesMap;
```

